    Class Description
    Address
    A patron's shipping address.
    Address.AddressField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the Address resource.
    BaseResource
    A superclass made to handle JSON deserialization for all the resources.
    Benefit
    A benefit added to the campaign, which can be added to a tier to be delivered to the patron.
    Benefit.BenefitField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the Benefit resource.
    Campaign
    The creator's page, and the top-level object for accessing lists of members, tiers, etc.
    Campaign.CampaignField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the Campaign resource.
    Deliverable
    The record of whether or not a patron has been delivered the benefit they are owed because of their member tier.
    Deliverable.DeliverableField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the Deliverable resource.
    Field
    An interface representing a field or property in any of the resources.
    Goal
    A funding goal in USD set by a creator on a campaign (Earnings-based goal).
    Goal.GoalField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the Goal resource.
    Media
    A file uploaded to patreon.com, usually an image.
    Media.MediaField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the Media resource.
    Member
    The record of a user's membership to a campaign.
    Member.MemberField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the Member resource.
    PaginationMeta
    A class representing the pagination meta for some responses.
    PatreonAPI
    An instance of the Patreon API.
    PledgeEvent
    The record of a pledging action taken by the user, or that action's failure.
    PledgeEvent.PledgeEventField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the PledgeEvent resource.
    Post
    Content posted by a creator on a campaign page.
    Post.PostField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the Post resource.
    RequestUtil
    A utility for making GET requests to Patreon's REST API.
    SocialConnections
    A mapping from the user's connected application names to external user id on the respective application.
    SocialConnections.UserIDObject
    An object containing the properties of the social connection.
    Tier
    A membership level on a campaign, which can have benefits attached to it.
    Tier.TierField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the Tier resource.
    User
    The Patreon user, which can be both patron and creator.
    User.UserField
    This enum represents the different fields or properties associated with the User resource.
